author: Gus_263
title: Good pack
review: A good pack, including five pieces too usable, like krana and kanohi nuva in assortment of shape and color. But, with the new pieces of toa metru, the nuva masks being small and the krana useless. Only in the old heads these masks looks like very cool. In others, no much. It is a pack with assortment, i rate it 4/5.
